Our Story
/$
$
R
oxy's Pub was established in 1933, serving West Palm Beach for almost 90 years . It's the ultimate neighborhood pub bar; where the locals hang out & play pool, darts or Jenga, grab a delicious bite to eat & enjoy an icy cold pint or fun craft drink.  Roxy's Pub offers a comfortable pub-like atmosphere featuring over 64 beers on tap & an extensive selection of spirits.  With twenty-two flat screens strategically placed throughout the restaurant, there isn’t a bad seat in the house for viewing sports. Our covered front patio offers table and booth seating with a large flat screen for those who enjoy being outside.
Our philosophy is simple: to provide great food, exceptional value, and friendly service to each and every customer we serve.
Cheers!

Roxy's Annual Block Parties
/$
$
Join us as we take over the 300 block of Clematis Street twice a year! We have two major block parties each year: one is a watch party for the Super Bowl, where we feature a giant jumbo-tron, beer trucks, portable bars & tons of seating to view the game, The other is of course our favorite holiday of the year: St Patrick's Day! Filled with green beer, drinks, games, DJ's & tons of entertainment.  Don't miss out, they're ALWAYS a blast!!!
